v class=\"tli-content tli-content-on\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2002.9<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">-</span>2007.7 &nbsp; 清华大学工程物理系（核科学与技术） &nbsp;博士</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2006.9-2007.2 &nbsp; 瑞士洛桑联邦理工学院EPFL &nbsp; &nbsp;交流学生</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2004.5-2005.1 &nbsp; 瑞士洛桑联邦理工学院EPFL &nbsp; &nbsp;交流学生</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>1998.9<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">-</span>2002.7 &nbsp; 清华大学工程物理系（工程物理专业）学士</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n</div></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2014-至今　清华大学工程物理系　副研究员</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2013.07-2013.08　欧洲核子研究中心CERN访问学者</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2010.03-2010.06 &nbsp; 瑞士洛桑联邦理工学院EPFL　访问学者</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2009-2014　清华大学工程物理系　助理研究员</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2008.02-2008.07 　欧洲核子研究中心CERN　访问学者</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2007-2009　清华大学物理系博士后</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span><br></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>《嵌入式实时操作系统与微控制器应用》（</span><a href=\"https://learn.tsinghua.edu.cn/f/wlxt/index/course/teacher/course?wlkcid=2022-2023-1144814682\" title=\"嵌入式实时系统与微控制器应用\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">60320024-0</span></a><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">），研究生30人/64学时</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>研究生指导：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">指导（协助指导）博士生5人、硕士生3人。</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">从事核电子学与系统控制方向的研究工作，主要包括可扩展读出电子学设计技术、高性能数字信号实时处理技术、大动态范围微弱信号测量技术、实时系统控制技术等方面的研究工作。</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2023年-2028年　中子信号采集系统研发技术服务，企事业委托项目，负责；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2021年-2025年　基于小型中子源研制具有宽𝑸范围和高流强增益的紧凑型聚焦小角中子散射谱仪，国家重大科研仪器研制项目，技术骨干；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2016年-2020年　高精度气体径迹探测器及激光校正的研究，国家自然科学基金重点项目，项目协作负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2015年-2018年　极低本底热中子探测技术研究，国家自然科学基金项目，负责；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2014年-2017年　研制超高纯锗晶体及其辐射探测器关键技术研究，国家自然科学基金项目，技术骨干；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2014年-2016年　涂硼稻草管阵列高性能多通道复用读出电子学系统研究，中物院中子物理学重点实验室开放基金，负责；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2011年-2013年　一种新型热中子位置灵敏涂硼稻草管探测器的研制，国家自然科学基金项目，负责；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2011年-2013年　先进探测器技术及应用研究，科工局核能开发科研项目，子课题负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2007年-2008年　大亚湾反应堆中微子实验电子学板的预制研究，中科院高能物理研究所，技术骨干。</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1. Hua, N; Gong, H; Liu, YN, A count correction method for multistage dead time in gamma-ray spectrometry,Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research A, 2023.1</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. Wei, Shuoyang; Gong, Hui; Song, Honghu; Hu, Ankang; Xiong, Jun; Zhang, Hui; Li, Junli; Qiu, Rui, An Active Dose Measurement Device for Ultra-short, Ultra-intense Laser Facilities，Health physics，2022.4</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">3. Jiang, ZG; Gong, H; Li, JM; Wang, XW; Wang, YQ，Development and performance evaluation of a multi-layer boron-lined detector for the CPHS-SANS instrument,JOURNAL OF APPLIED CRYSTALLOGRAPHY, Page 1738-1746, 2021.12</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4. Huang, Y; Gong, H; Li, J; Li, Y，Development of the readout system for a time projection chamber prototype, JOURNAL OF INSTRUMENTATION, 卷: 14, JAN 2019</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">5. Jiang, ZG; Gong, H; Li, JM; Wang, YQ; Wang, XW，Experimental study of a boron coated straw detector module at CPHS, JOURNAL OF INSTRUMENTATION, 卷: 13 , &nbsp;AUG 2018</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">6. Zeng, ZM; Gong, H; Yue, Q; Li, JM，A novel method to measure low flux ambient thermal neutrons with He-3 proportional counters，Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research A,卷: 866 &nbsp;页: 242-247, SEP 2017</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">7. Zeng, ZM; Gong, H; Li, JM; Yue, Q; Zeng, Z; Cheng, JP, Design of the thermal neutron detection system for CJPL-II，CHINESE PHYSICS C, &nbsp;卷: 41 &nbsp;期: 5, &nbsp;MAY 2017</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">8. Zeng, ZM; Gong, H; Yue, Q; Li, JM，Thermal neutron background measurement in CJPL，Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research A,卷804页108-112，Dec 2015</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">9. Y Hao，G Hui，J Li，Y Wang，X Wang，Y Li，K Kang , A multiplex readout method for position sensitive boron coated straw neutron detector, Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research A, 2015.10</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">10. Huang T.C., Gong H.,Shao B.B.,*Wang, X.W.,Zhang, Y.,Pang, B.B.，Development of 3He LPSDs andread-out system for the SANS spectrometer at CPHS，Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research A, 735卷, pp 374-378,2014</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">11. T.C. Huang, H.Gong, B.B.Shao, D.Wang, X.Z.Zhang, K.Zhang, J.Wei, X.W.Wang, X.L. Guan, C.-K.Loong, J.Z.Tao, L.Zhou, Y.B.Ke,Design of a new time-of-flight small-angle neutron scattering instrument at CPHS, Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research A，2012</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">12. Hui Gong, Yanchang Lin, Guanghua Gong, Tao Xue, Xi Wang, Beibei Shao, Shaomin Chen, Xiaonan Li, Zheng Wang, Qiuju Li,Design of the local trigger board for the Daya Bay reactor neutrino experiment, Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research A, 2011</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>著作：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">[1]“嵌入式实时操作系统μC/OS-III”，宫辉、曾鸣、龚光华、杜强、黄土琛等译，北京航空航天大学出版社，2012</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">[2]“单片机与嵌入式系统开发方法”，薛涛、宫辉等著，清华大学出版社，2009</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">[3]“嵌入式系统中的双核技术”，邵贝贝、宫辉等著，北京航空航天大学出版社，2008</span></p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    \n    \n    \n</form>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 end-->\n    <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n    <!--底部-